e stores.'=>'Dobrodošli v novem standardu za WooCommerce trgovine.','We hate complex configurations too. Get up and running with CheckoutWC in 5 minutes or less. ⚡️'=>'Tudi mi sovražimo zapletene nastavitve. Zaženite CheckoutWC v 5 minutah ali manj. ⚡️','Welcome to CheckoutWC 10.0'=>'Dobrodošli v CheckoutWC 10.0','CheckoutWC 10.0 is a major update with new features and optimizations to make your WooCommerce store run better.'=>'CheckoutWC 10.0 je velika posodobitev z novimi funkcijami in optimizacijami, ki bodo vašo WooCommerce trgovino naredile boljšo.','Just Say When'=>'Samo povej kdaj','Our new rules engine puts you in charge. Want to show an Order Bump only to first time customers who use a specific coupon code? You can do that. Want to show specific trust badges based on what is in the cart? You can do that too!'=>'Naš nov sistem pravil vam daje nadzor. Želite prikazati Order Bump samo prvim strankam, ki uporabijo določen kupon? To lahko storite. Želite prikazati določene značke zaupanja glede na vsebino košarice? Tudi to lahko storite!','Get Started Faster'=>'Začnite hitreje','Creating Order Bumps has lots of options. Our new Quick Start will help you get started faster.'=>'Ustvarjanje Order Bumpov ima veliko možnosti. Naš novi Hitri začetek vam bo pomagal začeti hitreje.','Configure Order Bumps'=>'Konfigurirajte Order Bumpe','And a lot more'=>'In še veliko več','To view the full list of changes, checkout our change log.'=>'Za ogled celotnega seznama sprememb si oglejte naš dnevnik sprememb.','Read Our Change Log'=>'Preberite naš dnevnik sprememb','Step 1: Activate Your License'=>'Korak 1: Aktivirajte svojo licenco','Step 1: Try CheckoutWC Premium Free For 7 Days'=>'Korak 1: Preizkusite CheckoutWC Premium brezplačno 7 dni','Enter your license key. An active license is required for all functionality.'=>'Vnesite svojo licenčno kodo. Aktivna licenca je potrebna za vse funkcionalnosti.','Supercharge your WooCommerce store.'=>'Pospešite svojo WooCommerce trgovino.'